invariant io_extra250.BufferedIOBase.class_is_abcmeta:
  description: "io.BufferedIOBase.__class__.__name__ == 'ABCMeta' — BufferedIOBase is an abstract base class; its metaclass is ABCMeta; verified Python 3.14.3 macOS"
  category: class_identity
